<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA515_03_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema515_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema515_03_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">잘못 계산한 부분을 찾아 이유를 쓰고, 옳게 계산해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center">
          <div class="tabbox_wrap align_center left">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="flex justify_center align_center gap_4">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>8</span>
                  <span>9</span>
                </div>
                +
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>6</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>16</span>
                  <span>18</span>
                </div>
                +
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>18</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>18</span>
                  <span>18</span>
                </div>
                = 1
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tabbox">
              <span class="tit_box" lang="y">이유</span>
              <div class="conts_box">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                  <div class="example_box">
                    <p lang="y">
                      <span class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                        <span class="fraction_txt">
                          <span class="fraction_box">
                            <span>1</span>
                            <span>6</span>
                          </span>
                          의 분모와 분자에 3을 곱하여 통분해야 하는데 분모에는 3, 분자
                        </span>
                        <span class="fraction_txt">에는 2를 곱하여 잘못 계산했습니다.</span>
                      </span>                      
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tabbox right">
            <strong class="tit_tabbox" lang="y">옳은 계산</strong>
            <div class="conts_tabbox">
              <div class="flex align_center justify_center gap_4">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>8</span>
                  <span>9</span>
                </div>
                +
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>6</span>
                </div>
                =
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="16"></math-field></div>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="18"></math-field></div>
                </div>
                <span>+</span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field></div>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="18"></math-field></div>
                </div>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="19"></math-field></div>
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="18"></math-field></div>
                </div>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="mixed_fraction">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1" class="w_80"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field></div>
                    <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="18"></math-field></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">분수를 통분할 때에는 분수의 분모와 분자에 같 은 수를 곱해야 합니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve">
              <!--  -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
